headlines.description: — Joel Embiid had 29 points, 11 rebounds and 10 assists in his first action in a month to lead the Philadelphia 76ers to a 118-116 victory Tuesday night over the Dallas Mavericks, who fell to 0-2 since trading star Luka Doncic to the Los Angeles Lakers.
headlines.shortLinkText: Joel Embiid has triple-double in 1st game in a month as Sixers slip past Mavs 118-116

headlines.description: — Jayson Tatum scored 22 points, Derrick White added 20 and the Boston Celtics showed their championship makeup down the stretch with a 112-105 win over the Cleveland Cavaliers on Tuesday night in a matchup of the Eastern Conference's top teams.
headlines.shortLinkText: Jayson Tatum scores 22, Celtics hold off Cavaliers 112-105 in matchup of Eastern Conference's best

headlines.description: — Keon Johnson and D'Angelo Russell made 3-pointers in the final 10 seconds, and the Brooklyn Nets stunned the Houston Rockets 99-97 on Tuesday night for their first home victory in two months.
headlines.shortLinkText: Late 3s by Johnson and Russell give the Nets a 99-97 win over the Rockets

events.name: New York Knicks at Toronto Raptors

headlines.description: — Karl-Anthony Towns had 27 points and 20 rebounds, Jalen Brunson scored 28 points and the New York Knicks held on to beat the Toronto Raptors 121-115 on Tuesday night for their eighth win in 10 games.
headlines.shortLinkText: Towns has 27 points and 20 rebounds as Knicks win eighth straight over Raptors, 121-115

headlines.description: — Rookie Matas Buzelis scored a career-best 24 points and Josh Giddey matched it to help the Chicago Bulls top the Miami Heat 133-124 on Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Josh Giddey, Matas Buzelis score 24 to lead the Bulls over the Heat 133-124

events.name: Los Angeles Lakers at LA Clippers

headlines.description: — LeBron James had 26 points, nine assists and eight rebounds, and Luka Doncic watched approvingly from the bench while the Los Angeles Lakers thrashed the Los Angeles Clippers 122-97 Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: LeBron scores 26, and the Lakers thrash the Clippers 122-97 with Luka Doncic watching on the bench

events.name: Indiana Pacers at Portland Trail Blazers

headlines.description: — Anfernee Simons had 22 points and the Portland Trail Blazers won their fifth straight game with a 112-89 victory over the Indiana Pacers on Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Simons scores 22 and Portland downs Indiana 112-89 for 5th straight win
